description:
Looking for heavy-duty RG6 cables?

These cables are perfect for TV access and even better if you're building a home entertainment system. Our cables can perform really well in high-frequency applications while also providing insulation and shielding to prevent distortion or interference. You won't be disappointed with our products!

The PVC jacket on the RG6 coaxial cable is robust and flexible, and it meets the CM and CL2 fire safety ratings. Heavy quad-shielding protects against electromagnetic interference (EMI) and radio frequency interference (RFI) using four layers of aluminum foil and braid shielding (RFI).

Come home to your favorite TV shows in high definition time. Seek a strong heart for transmission - RG6 6-pair cable supplies oxygen to transmission and data signals, enabling far-reaching transmissions of cable and Internet services without interference or interference.
